response.original_title: The Making Of Dzvinka: Tryzub's 50th Anniversary
response.overview: A story that started at age 11, Shane Gibson puts the story of Oleksa Dovbush on stage. For the 50th Anniversary of the Tryzub Ukrainian Dance Society, DZVINKA hits stage in 2024 and 2025.
response.title: The Making Of Dzvinka: Tryzub's 50th Anniversary
